cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically object detection and 3D pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of CAD models and geometric features suggests that the paper could also be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the focus on industrial objects and the use of a RANSAC-like algorithm suggests that the paper could also be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics).
